## ğŸ“Œ Features

- Instant weight calculation based on:
  - Aperture (OPG)
  - Wire Diameter (DIA)
  - Screen Width (Trim Dim 1)
  - Screen Length (Trim Dim 2)
- Clean and modern UI
- Calculation history stored in-session
- Fully client-side â€” works offline
- Ideal for manufacturing, quoting, and internal workflows

